News.Title: Arvee Laboratories India: Q3 Profit Drops 37.5% Amid Rising Expenses
News.Summary: Arvee Laboratories India reported Q3 FY25 results with revenue up 15.71% YoY to ₹8.91 crore, but profit down 37.5% to ₹0.15 crore. Operating income decreased 58.82% YoY. SG&A expenses rose 19.39% YoY. EPS fell 36.36% to ₹0.14.
